score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:32:36.000Z","msg":"please help us...."},{"pid":"1f80518ea4bcae35f2a94a7a925f704850c32bf4","tid":1476661,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"好似幾有用 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebe147128294d795fa7285414c44a1fc47e1b56","tid":1476661,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\nPostal code 就打000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPErM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=0a1f0762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"cc76bace0f9c380a5687f41032c06af096f53c1b","tid":1476661,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"求求00後都幫手簽, 對你地都有好處<br />\n<br />\n英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解要支持?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.成功爭取父母啲BNO變BC後, 因關係可以用家庭團聚形式入籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.增加香港有外國國籍啲人數, 提升外國政府啲話語權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.因中共反對, 所以我地更加要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.中共話香港人都是中國公民, 唔通你地想一世都係中國公民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPostal code 就打000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPErM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=0a1f0762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"c62d62c187cad34e88cfdd00cb3efd595421f1f9","tid":1476661,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2314cfada1afff379b5b99c169fc2654bddf503","tid":1476661,"uid":29799,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3104c12d5576c9d320c73b64f2bdf32c57890be3","tid":1476661,"uid":49258,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:42:57.000Z","msg":"低鳩能，示威叫人拎本passport 出嚟做乜撚嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:58:26.000Z","msg":"你就低鳩能, 比英國佬見到一定有用!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"Agree. <br />\n而家咩都要試, 咩都要做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a012961e6bfd0ba1ff880efacdd461a936964aa","tid":1476661,"uid":222482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"今次確實有機"},{"pid":"35fb97c90d9a8ed63e4e32e56df61f021880278d","tid":1476661,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"BNO變BC一定要有政治審查睇係咪支持民主自由等普世價值<br />\n唔可以所有人都就咁升格 藍絲應該留係地獄鬼國<br />\n<br />\n更好既選項係應該<span style=\"color: red;\">推動係英國劃地成立新香港自治區</span><br />\n即使冇BNO既手足都可以被救 要支持民主自由等西方普世價值既真香港人先允許有自治區居留權<br />\n二來自治區同英國本土區隔 可以減少對英國本土既影響 會易少少造成集體移民既效果"},{"pid":"b2d98b013ca526ec1a31ff7e9dce7721cec2fdda","tid":1476661,"uid":308875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"求求00後幫手簽, 對你地都有好處<br />\n英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解要支持?<br />\n1.成功爭取父母啲BNO變BC後, 因關係可以用家庭團聚形式入籍<br />\n2.增加香港有外國國籍啲人數, 提升外國政府啲話語權<br />\n3.因中共反對, 所以我地更加要支持<br />\n4.中共話香港人都是中國公民, 唔通你地想一世都係中國公民?<br />\n<br />\nPostal code: <a href=\"https://www.doogal.co.uk/AdministrativeAreas.php?district=E09000001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doogal.co.uk%2FAdministrativeAreas.php%3Fdistrict%3DE09000001&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPErM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=13cc4f3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.doogal.co.uk/AdministrativeAreas.php?district=E09000001</a><br />\n入面自己簡<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPErM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=0a1f0762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sv8SMgq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSv8SMgq.png&h=a99dfb75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d882dfc7d191f581b83a00225d11d659147ce9e","tid":1476661,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:52:55.000Z","msg":"過四萬了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CR1X1qy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCR1X1qy.png&h=e22a1ef7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8928308eac4ba896f00aaf409db03a30e32c7e3b","tid":1476661,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:39:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf4eba516338758f6116